1.Mounting phase/loading the components in the first time load/ rendering the components
2.Updating phase/ if any state change or props change that phase is updating phase
3.unmounting phase- removing the component from the DOM
4.Exception handling / Error handling/if anything happened to the children components as a parent
it should take care of the error boundary

